issue.body:
I'm getting the following error in the logs:

 [homebridge-eufy-robovac] This plugin slows down Homebridge. The read handler for the characteristic 'On' didn't respond at all!. Please check that you properly call the callback! See https://git.io/JtMGR for more info.

Connecting...
Robovac Error {}
Disconnected!
Connecting...
Robovac Error {}
Disconnected!

Is there anything I can do to diagnose this?

comment.body: This fork has the IP option and worked for me: https://github.com/ale770/homebridge-eufy-robovac

issue.title: Add ip address to options
issue.body: I was able to resolve this issue #41 and https://github.com/apexad/eufy-robovac/issues/31 by adding the local IP address of my vacuum cleaner to the config.
